[00:00.00]Cendres Demo
[00:03.00]灰烬 演示版
[00:05.25]演唱：Suno
[00:10.00]作词：LeoLee
[00:20.25]作曲：Suno
[00:25.00]制作：LeoLee
[00:35.00]专辑：《白色向日葵》x Suno
[00:44.50]An arrow came from the Sitian shore
[00:44.50]一支箭自锡蒂亚海岸飞来
[00:48.60]Through the Balkans, through the blood and gore
[00:48.60]穿过了巴尔干，穿过了血海
[00:51.77]It carried the sighs of Anatolia
[00:51.77]它驮着小亚细亚的叹息
[00:55.60]And half of Europe's hysteria
[00:55.60]和半个欧罗巴的癫狂
